Cream butter and sugar; add eggs. Sift dry ingredients 3 times; combine thoroughly with egg mixture. Add vanilla. Roll in waxed paper and store in refrigerator to chill thoroughly. Preheat oven to 375 degrees F (190 degrees C). Roll out dough very thin on well-floured board; cut with cookie cutter. Bake on greased cookie sheets for 6 - 10 minutes.